window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After defeating the hobgoblin threat, Oren is now faced with an even more tenacious enemy: the players themselves.&nbsp;</p> <p>His old guild have discovered his village's location and a deadly strike force is closing in. With time running out, Oren must build up his clan and recruit an army of monsters if he's to have any hope of withstanding the coming attack.&nbsp;</p> <p>The Soundbooth Theater Team for this production:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p></p> <ul> <li>Jeff Hays - Narration, music, and sound design&nbsp;</li> <li>Laurie Catherine Winkel - Raystia and Yulli&nbsp;</li> <li>Annie Ellicott - Misa and Kusitesh&nbsp;</li> <li>Dalton Lynne - Editing and proofing</li> <li>Griffin Malnar - Editing and mastering</li> </ul>"; 
